<div class="skills-content">
  <h2>Technologies</h2>

  <p>
    Here is a list of the thechnologies I have experience through my career as a software developer
    and I have been polishing through many different projects.
  </p>

  <div class="language-content">
    <div class="language-img-content">
      <img src="<%= image_path('ruby.svg') %>" alt="img">
    </div>
    <div class="language-description">
      <strong>Ruby</strong>
      <br>
      Ruby is an interpreted, high-level, general-purpose programming language. It was designed with
      an emphasis on programming productivity and simplicity. In Ruby, everything is an object, including primitive
      data types. It was developed in the mid-1990s by Yukihiro "Matz" Matsumoto in Japan.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="language-content right">
    <div class="language-img-content">
      <img src="<%= image_path('html.svg') %>" alt="html img">
    </div>
    <div class="language-description">
      <strong>HTML</strong>
      <br>
      The HyperText Markup Language, or HTML, is the standard markup language for documents designed to be displayed in
      a web browser. HTML describes the structure of a web page semantically and contains the building blocks of a web
      page.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="language-content">
    <div class="language-img-content">
      <img src="<%= image_path('css-3.svg') %>" alt="img">
    </div>
    <div class="language-description">
      <strong>CSS3</strong>
      <br>
      Cascading Style Sheets (CSS) is a style sheet language used for describing the presentation
      of a document written in a markup language such as HTML. CSS is a cornerstone technology of the World Wide Web.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="language-content right">
    <div class="language-img-content">
      <img src="<%= image_path('javascript.svg') %>" alt="img">
    </div>
    <div class="language-description">
      <strong>Javascript</strong>
      <br>
      JavaScript is a programming language that is one of the core technologies of the World
      Wide Web. All major web browsers have a dedicated engine to execute Javascript code on users' devices.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="language-content">
    <div class="language-img-content">
      <img src="<%= image_path('sql.svg') %>" alt="img">
    </div>
    <div class="language-description">
      <strong>SQL</strong>
      <br>
      Structured Query Language is a standardized programming language that is used to manage relational
      databases and perform various operations on the data in them.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
